{"tid":2387424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[股災來了] 諾輝健康破發討論區","createTime":"2021-01-30T10:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T10:08:14.000Z","uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"570eae7b288c6c65f6d9f33caa4c13d2db3eebb8","tid":2387424,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"內地癌症早期篩查產品製造商諾輝健康科技擬香港上市，市場消息指，公司已於周四（28日）通過上市聆訊，預計2月內上市，並計劃集資約3億美元（約23.4億港元），高盛、瑞銀為聯席保薦人。<br />\n<br />\n諾輝健康專注高發癌症居家早期篩查及基因檢測服務。目前公司已推出針對腸癌、宮頸癌、胃癌等居家早篩產品。公司產品及主要候選產品當中，兩種結直腸癌適應症的藥品已國家藥監局批准。截至2020年上半年，經調整淨虧損為5393萬（人民幣，下同），2019年同期為5590萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2623400/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E8%AB%BE%E8%BC%9D%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%80%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87%E7%B4%8423.4%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E3%80%812%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2623400%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2582%25A1IPO%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BC%259D%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%259B%2586%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%25B4%258423.4%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E3%2580%25812%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=fb86e840\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2623400/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E8%AB%BE%E8%BC%9D%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%80%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87%E7%B4%8423.4%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E3%80%812%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82</a>"},{"pid":"d50ef33709d9ebb06325bdee61504831a4263c66","tid":2387424,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯台"},{"pid":"786eafafb3d45e8aa5b14f4af01b00a50e3d67e0","tid":2387424,"uid":7439,